Dear exchanges, merchants, services, to reiterate, the wallet bug has been patched and the fix is included in the v0.14.0.1 tag. In addition, there will be a v0.14.0.2 tag soon, which will include some other bug fixes (e.g. the Ledger bug).

CLI v0.14.0.2 has been tagged!   https://t.co/hIOPMnYp8s  This release includes a patch for the wallet bug, a patch for the Ledger bug as well as some additional bug fixes.   - Release binaries are forthcoming. - GUI v0.14.0.0 release binaries are forthcoming as well.
Note that v0.14.0.2 will be a full release, i.e., one that includes release binaries as well. By contrast, v0.14.0.1 will merely remain a tag.

In addition and to reiterate, users, merchants, services, pool operators, exchanges, and any other members of the Monero ecosystem should upgrade to and subsequently run v0.14 in order to be sufficiently prepared.
